	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw' class='no-justify'><nobr><div>سُورَةُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> </div><div>المُجَادلَةِ</div></nobr></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِسۡمِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِ </div><div>ٱلرَّحِيمِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>قَدۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> سَمِعَ ٱللَّهُ قَوۡلَ ٱلَّتِي <a data-content='تحاورُك وتـُـراجعك الكلام' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>تُجَٰدِلُكَ</a> فِي زَوۡجِهَا وَتَشۡتَكِيٓ إِلَى </div><div>ٱللَّهِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَٱللَّهُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَسۡمَعُ <a data-content='مراجعتكما القوْل' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>تَحَاوُرَكُمَآۚ</a> إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ سَمِيعُۢ بَصِيرٌ ١ ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div><a data-content='يُحَرّمون نساءَهمْ تحريم أمّهاتهم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يُظَٰهِرُونَ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِنكُم</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِّن نِّسَآئِهِم مَّا هُنَّ أُمَّهَٰتِهِمۡۖ إِنۡ أُمَّهَٰتُهُمۡ إِلَّا </div><div>ٱلَّٰٓـِٔي</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَدۡنَهُمۡۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَإِنَّهُمۡ لَيَقُولُونَ <a data-content='فظيعا منه يُنكِره الشرع والعَقل' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>مُنكَرٗا مِّنَ ٱلۡقَوۡلِ</a> <a data-content='كذِبا باطلاً مُـنـحَرفا عن الحقّ' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَزُورٗاۚ</a> </div><div>وَإِنَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱللَّهَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَعَفُوٌّ غَفُورٞ ٢ وَٱلَّذِينَ يُظَٰهِرُونَ مِن نِّسَآئِهِمۡ ثُمَّ </div><div>يَعُودُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِمَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> قَالُواْ فَتَحۡرِيرُ رَقَبَةٖ مِّن قَبۡلِ أَن <a data-content='يستمْـتعا بالوقاع أو دواعيه' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يَتَمَآسَّاۚ</a> ذَٰلِكُمۡ </div><div>تُوعَظُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِهِۦۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعۡمَلُونَ خَبِيرٞ ٣ فَمَن لَّمۡ يَجِدۡ فَصِيَامُ </div><div>شَهۡرَيۡنِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مُتَتَابِعَيۡنِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِن قَبۡلِ أَن يَتَمَآسَّاۖ فَمَن لَّمۡ يَسۡتَطِعۡ فَإِطۡعَامُ </div><div>سِتِّينَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِسۡكِينٗاۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ذَٰلِكَ لِتُؤۡمِنُواْ بِٱللَّهِ وَرَسُولِهِۦۚ وَتِلۡكَ حُدُودُ </div><div>ٱللَّهِۗ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلِلۡكَٰفِرِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌ ٤ إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ <a data-content='يعادون ويشاقّـون ويخالفون' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>يُحَآدُّونَ</a> ٱللَّهَ </div><div>وَرَسُولَهُۥ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='أذلـّـوا أو أهلكوا أو لعِنوا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>كُبِتُواْ</a> كَمَا كُبِتَ ٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبۡلِهِمۡۚ وَقَدۡ أَنزَلۡنَآ ءَايَٰتِۢ بَيِّنَٰتٖۚ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>بَيِّنَٰتٖۚ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلِلۡكَٰفِرِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَذَابٞ مُّهِينٞ ٥ يَوۡمَ يَبۡعَثُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ جَمِيعٗا </div><div>فَيُنَبِّئُهُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِمَا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَمِلُوٓاْۚ <a data-content='أحاط به عِلما' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أَحۡصَىٰهُ ٱللَّهُ</a> وَنَسُوهُۚ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ شَهِيدٌ </div><div>٦</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
